'''薩凡納大區'''（{{lang-en|Savannah Region}}）是[[加納|加納]]的{{le|大區 (迦納)|Regions of Ghana|大區}}，位於該國中北部，首府{{le|達蒙哥|Damongo}}，北鄰[[西北大區_(加納)|西北大區]]，南毗[[博諾大區|博諾大區]]和[[東博諾大區|東博諾大區]]，西臨[[東北大區_(加納)|東北大區]]和[[北部大區_(加納)|北部大區]]，面積35,862平方公里，2021年人口653,266人。

==歷史==
2018年12月27日{{le|2018年迦納新大區公民投票|2018 Ghanaian new regions referendum|迦納新大區公民投票}}中<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.ghanaweb.com/GhanaHomePage/NewsArchive/Referendum-Massive-YES-votes-for-6-new-regions-711692|title=Referendum: Massive YES votes for 6 new regions {{!}} General News 2018-12-28|website=www.ghanaweb.com|date=28 December 2018|access-date=2019-01-02|archive-date=2022-01-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220131080132/https://www.ghanaweb.com/GhanaHomePage/NewsArchive/Referendum-Massive-YES-votes-for-6-new-regions-711692|dead-url=no}}</ref>，以同意票206,350票（99.52%）、投票率81.77%通過由[[北部大區_(加納)|北部大區]]分出新設薩凡納大區案<ref>{{cite news | url=https://www.ghanabusinessnews.com/2018/12/29/all-six-proposed-regions-meet-constitutional-threshold-requirements-ec/ | title=All six proposed regions meet constitutional threshold requirements – EC | newspaper=Ghana Business News | date=29 December 2018 | accessdate=2022-01-31 | archive-date=2022-01-31 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220131080102/https://www.ghanabusinessnews.com/2018/12/29/all-six-proposed-regions-meet-constitutional-threshold-requirements-ec/ | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.graphic.com.gh/news/politics/confirmed-results-of-the-2018-referendum-on-new-regions.html|title=CONFIRMED: Results of the 2018 Referendum on new regions|last=Zurek|first=Kweku|website=Graphic Online|language=en-gb|access-date=2019-01-02|date=2018-12-28|archive-date=2021-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211111111152/https://www.graphic.com.gh/news/politics/confirmed-results-of-the-2018-referendum-on-new-regions.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.pulse.com.gh/news/local/referendum-6-new-regions-get-massive-yes-votes/6l8qds7|title=Referendum: 6 new regions get massive 'YES' votes|date=2018-12-28|website=www.pulse.com.gh|language=en-US|access-date=2019-01-02|archive-date=2022-01-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220131060354/https://www.pulse.com.gh/news/local/referen